《'''公报'''》（{{lang-en|''The Gazette''}}），中文全称《'''盖拉克斯公报'''》（The Galax Gazette），是一份[[美国|美国]][[半周刊|半周刊]]（semi-weekly）[[报纸|报纸]]<ref name="Commission1972">{{cite book|author=United States. Federal Communications Commission|title=Federal Communications Commission Reports: Decisions, Reports, and Orders of the Federal Communications Commission of the United States|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=u4qZAAAAIAAJ&pg=PA481|year=1972|publisher=U.S. Government Printing Office|pages=481–|access-date=2020-07-02|archive-date=2020-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200713000556/https://books.google.com/books?id=u4qZAAAAIAAJ&pg=PA481|dead-url=no}}</ref>，位于[[弗吉尼亚州|弗吉尼亚州]][[蓋拉克斯_(維吉尼亞州)|蓋拉克斯]]。该报隶属于[[兰德马克社区报纸股份有限公司|兰德马克社区报纸股份有限公司]]（Landmark Community Newspapers Inc.）<ref>{{cite book|title=Benn's Media|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=zDPjAAAAMAAJ|year=2002|publisher=Benn Business Information Services|pages=152–|access-date=2020-07-02|archive-date=2020-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200714122458/https://books.google.com/books?id=zDPjAAAAMAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
==发展历程==
《盖拉克斯公报》的前身是1924年成立的《[[格雷森·卡罗尔公报|格雷森·卡罗尔公报]]》（Grayson-Carroll Gazette），该报由[[格雷森·卡罗尔|格雷森·卡罗尔]]（Grayson Gazette）创办<ref name="FieldsHughes1976">{{cite book|author1=Bettye-Lou Fields|author2=Jene Hughes|title=Grayson County: A History in Words and Pictures|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=QSkSAAAAYAAJ|year=1976|publisher=Grayson County Historical Society|pages=315–|access-date=2020-07-02|archive-date=2020-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200802023227/https://books.google.com/books?id=QSkSAAAAYAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>，每周发行三次，这份报纸于1936年停刊<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.loc.gov/item/sn95079186|title=Grayson-Carroll Gazette (Galax, Va.) 1924-1936|accessdate=2020-07-02|publisher=[[Library_of_Congress|Library of Congress]]|archive-date=2020-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200831052540/https://www.loc.gov/item/sn95079186|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1937年，《格雷森·卡罗尔公报》更名为《盖拉克斯公报》（Galax Gazette），每周发行三次，1993年停刊<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.loc.gov/item/sn95079192|title=Galax Gazette (Galax, Va.) 1937-1993|accessdate=2020-07-02|publisher=[[Library_of_Congress|Library of Congress]]|archive-date=2020-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200904054516/https://www.loc.gov/item/sn95079192/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1994年，《盖拉克斯公报》（Galax Gazette）更名为《公报》（The Gazette），由兰德马克社区报纸股份有限公司发行<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.loc.gov/item/sn99066749/|title=The Gazette (Galax, Va.) 1994-Current|accessdate=2020-07-02|publisher=[[Library_of_Congress|Library of Congress]]|archive-date=2020-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200704084601/https://www.loc.gov/item/sn99066749/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1998年10月29日，《盖拉克斯公报》网络版上线<ref>{{cite web|url=https://whois.domaintools.com/galaxgazette.com|title=GalaxGazette.com WHOIS, DNS, & Domain Info – DomainTools|accessdate=2020-07-02|publisher=[[WHOIS|WHOIS]]|archive-date=2020-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200702131055/https://whois.domaintools.com/galaxgazette.com|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

